10 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 62 O.S. 2021, Section 203, is
11 amended to read as follows:
12 Section 203. A. Except as otherwise provided by subsection B
13 of this section, all monies that may come into the State Treasury,
14 pursuant to the provisions of Section 201 et seq. of this title,
15 together with all amounts that may be received by the State
16 Treasurer as investment income or as interest on average daily bank
17 balances, including investment income or interest on deposits from
18 funds deposited to the credit of the Constitutional Reserve Fund
19 created pursuant to Section 23 of Article X of the Oklahoma
20 Constitution, shall be apportioned and credited to the General
21 Revenue Fund for the current year.
22 B. The provisions of subsection A of this section shall not
23 apply to:
